pushing and shoving
to get off the plane.

538
00:28:03,812 --> 00:28:05,727
Are you sure
you're okay?Yeah.

539
00:28:05,771 --> 00:28:08,512
Ah, this is my son, Jason.

540
00:28:08,556 --> 00:28:09,949
I'm Craig Johnson.

541
00:28:09,992 --> 00:28:11,907
Oh. Katherine Parker.

542
00:28:11,951 --> 00:28:13,213
Katherine Parker.

543
00:28:13,996 --> 00:28:16,738
Say, uh...
Katherine Parker

544
00:28:16,782 --> 00:28:20,176
from Valley View
Elementary School?

545
00:28:21,482 --> 00:28:22,613
Yes.

546
00:28:24,659 --> 00:28:27,488
We were in Miss Miller's
third grade class together.

547
00:28:28,924 --> 00:28:30,752
Don't you remember,
we used to...

