00:33:36,318 --> 00:33:39,104
Okay, let's see,
shopping in the airport.

664
00:33:39,147 --> 00:33:40,888
How about a travel toothbrush?

665
00:33:40,931 --> 00:33:42,150
GIRLS: No!

666
00:33:42,194 --> 00:33:44,065
KATHERINE: Okay,
a couple of mats?

667
00:33:44,109 --> 00:33:45,849
Boring!

668
00:33:45,893 --> 00:33:47,068
How about a pill box?

669
00:33:47,112 --> 00:33:48,591
BOTH: no!

670
00:33:48,635 --> 00:33:50,463
All right, well,
we'll see you guys later.

671
00:33:50,506 --> 00:33:51,899
Oh. Uh...Okay, come on, girls.

672
00:33:51,942 --> 00:33:54,336
Katherine...Come on.

673
00:33:54,380 --> 00:33:55,685
Kath...

674
00:34:07,262 --> 00:34:08,655
How is your mother?

675
00:34:09,438 --> 00:34:10,570
Fine.

676
00:34:11,788 --> 00:34:13,616
How's everything
working at the house?

677
00:34:13,660 --> 00:34:15,792
Fine.

678
00:34:15,836 --> 00:34:20,014
You remember to run
a little water so the pipes
don't freeze while you're gone?

679
00:34:20,058 --> 00:34:21,059
Fine.

680
00:34:21,929 --> 00:34:23,148
Was I supposed to do that?

681
00:34:23,887 --> 00:34:25,324
Yes, of course.

682
00:34:29,154 --> 00:34:30,285
Oh...

683
00:34:31,373 --> 00:34:32,461
