00:34:39,425 --> 00:34:41,035
[LAUGHS]

687
00:34:42,254 --> 00:34:44,473
I remember this party.

688
00:34:48,347 --> 00:34:50,914
Scout's first birthday.

689
00:34:50,958 --> 00:34:54,309
God! It was before
Ellie was born.

690
00:34:57,791 --> 00:35:01,055
Oh, I used to love
those hardwood floors.

691
00:35:01,099 --> 00:35:03,057
