692
00:35:03,101 --> 00:35:04,667
Because Ellie
started crawling.

693
00:35:04,711 --> 00:35:06,930
Oh, that's right, the wood
was hard on her little knees.

694
00:35:06,974 --> 00:35:08,018
Yeah.

695
00:35:09,237 --> 00:35:11,457
Well, nothing much to
remember about that.

696
00:35:11,500 --> 00:35:13,198
MATT: Wait, wait,
not so fast.

697
00:35:16,026 --> 00:35:18,855
I remember a beautiful bride,

698
00:35:18,899 --> 00:35:21,815
and a lucky groom,
and a wonderful day,

699
00:35:21,858 --> 00:35:23,251
with lots of snow.

700
00:35:24,861 --> 00:35:26,559
More like a snow job.

701
00:35:26,602 --> 00:35:29,257
'Cause I remember making some
vows, and they didn't include

702
00:35:29,301 --> 00:35:33,435
