in the world
to go through this.

709
00:35:51,888 --> 00:35:52,933
Look at your parents.

710
00:35:53,716 --> 00:35:54,891
My parents?

711
00:35:54,935 --> 00:35:56,371
They could have
worked something out

712
00:35:56,415 --> 00:35:58,068
