couldn't remember a thing.

733
00:37:14,536 --> 00:37:16,756
Oh, honey, don't cry.

734
00:37:16,799 --> 00:37:20,586
Your mom and dad had
wonderful times together.
Tons of them.

735
00:37:20,629 --> 00:37:23,197
Even if they are too stubborn
to admit it.

736
00:37:24,329 --> 00:37:26,287
Grandma?

737
00:37:26,331 --> 00:37:28,985
You think they still
love each other?

738
00:37:29,029 --> 00:37:30,465
