from his second.

878
00:44:27,577 --> 00:44:29,492
Stepson from his third.

879
00:44:30,842 --> 00:44:32,887
Me, pretty simple.

880
00:44:33,758 --> 00:44:36,282
One wife, two burial plots.

881
00:44:36,325 --> 00:44:38,066
